  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: c72c9706ba29a9d428084a4a0a43db7f, type: 3}
  m_Name: Path_1_aftermath_dialogue
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueObject
  dialogue:
  - "Now all that is left is to wait for the plans and investigation to come to effect.\n\nLet\u2019s
    wait a while and see what they manage to do."
  - '...


    ...


    ...'
  - "Advisor! The sewer situation has been resolved.\n\nSecurity chief Parker reported
    in. They were able to establish how the crime was done and traced it back to
    the local factory owner.\n\nHe\u2019s looking at hefty fines for that.\n\nShame
    about the sewer itself though. The spill has affected the water quality of the
    river and will continue to do so in the future."
  - "<b>Disaster management ++:</b>\nThe toxic waste culprit was caught and won't
    be an issue in the future.\n\n<b>Satisfaction +:</b>\nThe story of consequences
    for major environmental crimes has improved citizens' mood.\n\n<b>Water resources
    --:</b> \nThe water quality of the river was affected and some parts of it are
    less usable."
